org.gbif.dwc.validator.result

Interface ResultAccumulatorIF

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileWriterResultAccumulator, ThresholdResultAccumulator

    public interface ResultAccumulatorIF
    Accumulate results from various validations. Implementations must the thread-safe after initialization. In other words, once created, the object can be shared among different threads to accumulate results.
    Author:
    cgendreau
